---
title: Pesto Mozzarella Flatbread with Vinaigrette Salad and Grape Tomatoes
description: Juicy heirloom tomatoes, rich pesto, and tender bell peppers top these flatbreads. A flourish of mozzarella and sprinkling of chilli flakes add a creamy and spicy kick!
